### Test Address API Endpoints
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7062
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login to get token (replace with actual user credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Get all addresses
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/address
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Add new address - CORRECT FORMAT
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/address
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Home",
  "address": "123 Main Street, Apartment 4B",
  "city": "New York",
  "pincode": "123456",
  "isDefault": true
}

### 4. Add another address
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/address
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Work",
  "address": "456 Business Ave, Suite 200",
  "city": "New York", 
  "pincode": "654321",
  "isDefault": false
}

### 5. Update address (replace {id} with actual address ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/user/address/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Home",
  "address": "789 Updated Street, Unit 5C",
  "city": "Brooklyn",
  "pincode": "111222",
  "isDefault": true
}

### 6. Delete address (replace {id} with actual address ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/user/address/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}